@539 = ~Instead of chasing skirts, you should be at home with your child, Coran.~
@540 = ~You don't want your daughter to become as... disdainful as her father.~
@541 = ~Ah, such harsh words coming from the luscious lips of a beautiful woman.~
@542 = ~There are many things you cannot control in life, and this may be one of those cases.~
@543 = ~I would not be welcome in my daughter's life, but I will cherish her from afar.~
@544 = ~And lastly, the mention of my daughter on your tongue is the last I'll tolerate.~